Package: UtilsR
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for Data Exploration and System Diagnostics
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Yuhao", "Ouyang", email = "ouyangyuhao@outlook.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for interactive data exploration,
    variable inspection, missing value analysis, system resource monitoring,
    and object size profiling. Provides S3 generic 'lv()' for summarizing
    variables in data.frames and Seurat objects, 'na_check()' for data quality
    analysis, and system diagnostics tools.
